有内涵的时政新媒体。
Connotation of the new political media.
澎湃新闻记者 南博一3月9日起，韩国政府开始实施口罩限购措施，每人每周限购两只。
The government has imposed a two-a-week cap on the purchase of face masks since March 9.
据韩联社3月9日报道，根据韩国政府公布的限购措施，韩国民众可按照出生年份尾数前往定点销售处购买口罩，每人每周限购两只，每只口罩售价均为1500韩元（约合8.6人民币）。
South Korean consumers can buy face masks at designated sales outlets according to the number of years of birth, each selling for 1,500 won (8.6 yuan) a week, the newspaper said.
措施规定，以民众出生年份尾数为准，周一限出生年份尾数为1和6的人购买，周二限尾数为2和7的人购买……以此类推，周五限尾数为5和0的人购买，周末不限。
Measures specify that purchases should be made on the basis of the number of calendar years of birth, Monday for those with 1 and 6 birthdays, and Tuesday for those with a residual number of 2 and 7.
购买口罩时民众须出示居民登记证、驾照、护照等有效身份证件。
People are required to produce valid identity documents such as residence registration, driver's license and passport when purchasing masks.
销售点会确认购买者的身份证和购买记录，每人每周只能购买两只。
The point of sale confirms the identity card and purchase record of the purchaser and can only buy two per person per week.
在户口登记簿上登记为共同居住的人员还可为10周岁以下的儿童和80周岁以上的老年人代买口罩。
Persons registered as co-residents in the household register may also buy masks for children under 10 years of age and older persons over 80 years of age.
代买口罩以代买对象的出生年份尾数为准，代买者须出示有效身份证和居民登记证副本。
Purchases of face masks are based on the number of years of birth of the subject, and the purchaser should produce a valid identity card and a copy of the resident registration card.
此外，除首尔和京畿道地区外，其他地区的邮局和农协超市也销售口罩。
In addition, in addition to Seoul and Gyeonggi Province, post offices and ACAP supermarkets in other regions also sell masks.
在邮局和农协超市的身份确认系统建立完成前，不论出生年份尾数，民众每人每日均可购买1只口罩。
Before the establishment of an identification system for post offices and the Association's supermarkets, each person can buy a mask every day, regardless of the number of years of birth.
预计身份确认系统建设将在本周内完成。
Construction of the identification system is expected to be completed within this week.
